Amanda Holden, 51, and her co-host Ashley Roberts, 40, had fun this morning as they took part in Heart FM’s sports day.The duo looked great in their skin-tight fitness gear which consisted of tiny red cycling shorts and white T-shirts with the Heart logo emblazoned on the chest.In a reel shared to Heart’s official Instagram account, Amanda and Ashley showed off their sporting credentials as they warmed up and practised the egg and spoon race.The caption joked: “Sports day chaos @noholdenback @iamashleyroberts.” Amanda also shared the comical clip to her Story and joked: "Mand down!"